OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Ffine end to the day with plenty of
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells, some
OL,9,Fpatchy cloud and light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FContinuing largely fine, dry
OL,12,Fand settled, some thicker cloud around
OL,13,Fat times, perhaps with the odd spot of
OL,14,Fdrizzle over the Lake District first
OL,15,Fthing. Feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
